        <prompt>What was the primary purpose of "Redemption Constitutions"?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">To restrict African American rights and reduce state spending</option>
            <option letter="b">To protect civil rights</option>
            <option letter="c">To expand public education</option>
            <option letter="d">To increase voter participation</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>Redemption Constitutions were adopted by Southern states to restrict African American rights and reduce state spending on public services after Reconstruction.</explanation>
