        <prompt>How did the "Labor Contract Laws" affect freed people?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">Required annual labor contracts and restricted mobility</option>
            <option letter="b">Provided fair labor conditions</option>
            <option letter="c">Increased wages</option>
            <option letter="d">Protected worker rights</option>
